  "description": "Celebrate with the ultimate Lake Travis bachelorette party boat cruise in Austin at Premier Party Cruises. Our ATX Disco Cruise offers three fabulous packages designed for bachelorette celebrations: Basic Bach at $85 per person includes professional DJ, photographer, and all party essentials; Disco Queen at $95 per person is our most popular package with the bride cruising FREE with 16+ guests; Super Sparkle Platinum at $105 per person includes VIP treatment, personal unicorn float, mimosa setup, and the bride cruises FREE with 16+ guests. Every bachelorette party cruise features a 4-hour Lake Travis experience with professional DJ, professional photographer capturing Instagram-worthy moments, BYOB cooler setup with ice, giant lily pad floats, party decorations, and an amazing party atmosphere with other bachelorette groups. Perfect for groups of 20-40+ guests. Also available: private boat rentals for intimate celebrations ranging from 14-75 person capacity.",
